Subject: Migrating Database to New SQL Server
Description:
Hi team

We are using StealthAudit v 11.5 and we are planning on migrating the DB currently hosted on a 2012 SQL server to a 2022 SQL server.

Can you advise what steps are required to be followed when performing this task?

Regards
Mark
Solution_Comment__c: StealthAUDIT scans the tsv files provided by SAM. If the SAM output is configured to keep log files longer than the data you already had for a previous backup, we can scan that data and restore activity information for days that were missed due to rollback.
